'''歐洲太空營運中心'''（{{lang-en|European Space Operations Centre}}）是[[欧洲空间局|欧洲空间局]]（ESA）的主要任务控制中心，位于[[德国|德国]][[达姆施塔特|达姆施塔特]]。歐洲太空營運中心的主要任务是代表欧洲空间局和{{tsl|en|Launch and Early Orbit Phases}}（LEOP）操控无人飞船并执行一些第三方任务。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Operations/SEMVKB8ZMRE_0.html |title=ESA Spacecraft Operations - About us & frequently asked questions |access-date=2016-10-05 |archive-date=2012-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031082015/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Operations/SEMVKB8ZMRE_0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 该中心还与欧洲空间局的国际合作伙伴和工厂负责着地面系统的工程、软件开发、飞行动力学和导航、任务控制工具和技术，空间碎片的研究开发合作业务等一系列合作。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/ESOC/SEM5LXFTFQG_0_ov.html |title=ESA’s Ground Systems Engineering Team |access-date=2016-10-05 |archive-date=2012-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121119050204/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/ESOC/SEM5LXFTFQG_0_ov.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

歐洲太空營運中心目前的主要任务包括恒星与行星的研究（如[[火星快車號|火星快車號]]和[[羅塞塔號|羅塞塔號]]）、天文学和基础物理学（如[[盖亚任务|盖亚任务]]和[[XMM-牛顿卫星|XMM-牛顿卫星]]）和地球观测任务（如{{tsl|en|CryoSat-2||CryoSat2}}和{{tsl|en|Swarm (spacecraft)||Swarm (spacecraft)}}）。營運中心还负责着{{tsl|en|ESTRACK|ESTRACK|ESTRACK网络}}地面站的开发、运营和维护。Teams at the Centre are also involved in research and development related to advanced mission control concepts and Space Situational Awareness, and standardisation activities related to frequency management; mission operations; tracking, telemetry and telecommanding; and [[太空垃圾|太空垃圾]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Operations/SEMVKB8ZMRE_0.html|title=About Operations|accessdate=2016-10-05|last=esa|archive-date=2012-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031082015/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Operations/SEMVKB8ZMRE_0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

